  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the fact is, that was a terrible time, because you were-- you didn't-- you were not allowed to see your child.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Which I don't think there was a country in the world where-- where-- where you couldn't see a little child that is sick.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was another problem, that my husband wanted John always to speak only Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So the few words that John knew were only Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so John couldn't communicate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, although he wasn't speaking a lot, but he still could say something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I really didn't know, either he's paralyzed, either he's can't speak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Either he can-- look, it was a terrible time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Until one day--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
